     <div>
      <h1>
       Welcome!
      </h1>
      <p>
       We welcome all those students of UCMerced who would
              like to learn more about (and do!) philosophy. Students at UC Merced
              can both
       <a href="http://philo.ucmerced.edu/minor.html">
        minor
       </a>
       and
       <a href="http://philo.ucmerced.edu/major.html">
        major
       </a>
       in philosophy. Use the navigation bar at the top of the
              page to access information about faculty, courses, events,
              and online philosophy resources.
      </p>
     </div>
